text: Eunidia fuscovittata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Stephan von Breuning in 1939. It is known from Kenya, the Ivory Coast, and Uganda.BioLib.cz - Eunidia fuscovittata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1939
